title: Patriots-Cowboys Stats
text:
___ INDIVIDUAL STATISTICS 
RUSHING_New England, Blount 13-74, Lewis 6-34, Brady 2-3, Garoppolo 2-(minus 2). Dallas, Randle 15-60, Weeden 3-18, McFadden 5-16, Michael 1-6. 
PASSING_New England, Brady 20-27-0-275. Dallas, Weeden 26-39-1-188. 
RECEIVING_New England, Lewis 8-59, Edelman 4-120, Gronkowski 4-67, Martin 2-23, Amendola 2-6. Dallas, McFadden 9-62, Witten 5-33, Beasley 4-40, Randle 4-13, Williams 2-30, Street 1-13, Whitehead 1-(minus 3). 
MISSED FIELD GOALS_None.
